I"<p>12 Reasons to Add Green Mango (Kairi) to Your Diet In Summer</p>

<p>There’s a reason raw mangoes make us think fondly of summers in India. Hailed as the king of fruits, these are a powerhouse of nutrition and very high in Vitamin C too. Mangoes are available in various colours around the world but the green ones are essential for treating digestive problems and losing weight. Below, we’ll discuss the nutritional content of raw mangoes, its health benefits, and various other things you need to know.</p>
